<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h4>
    <p>Your trip request was submitted successfully. We have sent your request to our drivers for a quick evaluation. You can check for their responses and your request status on your trips dashboard.</p>
     <br/>
    <p><b>Pickup Address:</b> <%= @trip.pickup_address %> </p>
    <p><b>Destination Address:</b> <%=  @trip.destination_address %></p>
    <p><b>Pickup Date:</b> <%= @trip.pickup_date %> </p>
    <p><b>Pickup Time:</b>  <%= @trip.pickup_time %></p>
    <p><b>Estimated Price:</b> <%= @trip.driver_fee %>  </p>
    <a href="https://wehaul.netlify.com" target="_blank">Log In</a>
    <br/>
    <p>Best</p>
    <p>WeHaul Team</p>
  </body>
</html>